{"tid":539816,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"嶺大SU聯署聲明撐陳劉 何君堯話要「家法侍候」！","createTime":"2018-01-25T01:47:59.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-25T03:10:18.000Z","uid":39464,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"d2ba2e04cdc9077d6d1e48bcb42c35b1b2d9ead5","tid":539816,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T01:47:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180125/large/1516815530_8be6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180125%2Flarge%2F1516815530_8be6.png&h=9c22df49&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一石激起千重浪，浸會大學對兩名佔領語文中心的學生作暫時停學處分，隨即惹起各界激辯。多間大專院校學生會及學聯，就浸大決定對陳、劉二人處以即時暫時停學處分發聯署聲明，表示嚴正抗議和極為遺憾，促各大學校長挺身捍衞言論和學術自由，當中包括嶺南大學學生會。不過，有關聲明卻被嶺大校董、立法會議員何君堯，以「家法侍候」為題轉載到其Facebook專頁，稱各大院校不單止要對行為不檢的學生予以懲處，「還要罷免那些是非不分的學生會幹事！」<br />\n<br />\n香港眾志成員周庭是浸大四年級生，則表示對浸大將兩人停學的決定感極度憤怒。周庭強調，粗言並非爭議重點，取消普通話及格作為畢業要求才是焦點，這個要求亦是多數浸大同學共識，校方卻置之不理，反而倉卒武斷給予停學處分，「身為教育工作者，卻一直做反教育的事」。<br />\n<br />\n周庭指出，浸大學生反對普通話為畢業要求「始歷多時」，經過多輪溝通、經過全民公投表達學生訴求、出席教務會議表達意見後，才直接走到語文中心，要求與高層對話；用過種種方法表達，卻換來校方轉移視線，完全無視同學意見。「當院校自主瀕臨淪陷，我們仍只執著學生粗口而忽視威權體制對大專院校施加壓力，是見樹不見林」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180125/57750942\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180125%2F57750942&d=lYIdUSeY49PtrXZ8XFOxu%2FjR1yQ20Y%2BboumAcDwsk0E%3D&h=99a76caa\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180125%2F57750942&h=3390a18e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180125/57750942</a>"},{"pid":"e95f76e54d44aadeebd5bac85513b4e8b284b6b2","tid":539816,"uid":389,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T01:48:44.000Z","msg":"家法殺無赦<br />\n正義屌老母"},{"pid":"17e2f185ed99222de58c000b7a302b0ea6e90e8a","tid":539816,"uid":63154,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T01:50:42.000Z","msg":"問何生係咪要殺無赦？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad7d5e4846ff7fc3be0612193ffeb06c41f59bd3","tid":539816,"uid":65743,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T03:02:26.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">殺右無赦</span></span>"},{"pid":"1f745370dc19e84a27d1944cea3bb9adc41eea1a","tid":539816,"uid":77196,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T03:04:26.000Z","msg":"你講殺人都未死啦，果兩個講下粗口有幾閒"},{"pid":"0eff4ee43f97c0b3ee763ad8164e82d793e7dea0","tid":539816,"uid":47005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T03:05:56.000Z","msg":"嘩, 好驚好不安wor, 黑社會呀？"},{"pid":"7a18ef59659c91a974b34ea5fdaa9a4eece90d6b","tid":539816,"uid":77959,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T03:09:35.000Z","msg":"何生又殺無赦，又家法伺候<br />\n我好驚喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係咪威脅緊我"},{"pid":"613533f12915ea188940a6944654f904bd0396b6","tid":539816,"uid":18385,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T03:10:18.000Z","msg":"周庭冇割席<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n要投周庭了"}]}